       "itertools.dropwhile.__iter__.__qualname__.__len__() == 18 — __qualname__ is 'dropwhile.__iter__' which has 18 characters; len('dropwhile.__iter__') == 18; new to extra137"]
    - [dropwhile_next_qualname_eq,
