       "itertools.dropwhile.__next__.__qualname__.__eq__('dropwhile.__next__') == True — dropwhile.__next__ is a slot method on the C type; its qualname is 'dropwhile.__next__'; str.__eq__('dropwhile.__next__') returns True; new to extra137"]
    - [dropwhile_next_qualname_len_eq_18,
       "dropwhile.__next__.__qualname__.__len__",
       [],
